      • checkOutAReservationUI

        private void checkOutAReservationUI​(int choice)
                             throws InvalidDateTimeFormatException
        Displays the UI for checking out a reservation and making payment.
        Parameters:
        choice - The choice of how user wants to find a reservation. 1 stands for by guest name, 2 stands for by guest contact number. If no valid choice is given, the method will exit.
        Throws:
        InvalidDateTimeFormatException - If the date and time format is invalid.

      • makePayment

        Parameters:
        totalAmount - The total amount of bill.
        guest - The guest who is paying the bill.
        Returns:
        the String of payment details.

      • getCorrectGuestName

        private java.util.List<Guest> getCorrectGuestName​(java.lang.String guestName)
        Asks for the user to enter the guest name and returns the list of guests with matching name. If the user enters a name that is not found in the record for 3 times, it returns null.
        Parameters:
        guestName - guest name
        Returns:
        list of guests with matching name if found with in 3 tries, null otherwise
